<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$DKinBJ" href="/people/DKinBJ">邓柯</a>，<strong title="我们都是虫子" class="zu-question-my-bio">我们都是虫子</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="9">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$snowyconcerto" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/snowyconcerto" class="zg-link" title="Snowy Concerto">Snowy Concerto</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$li-jia-hui-99-20" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/li-jia-hui-99-20" class="zg-link" title="李嘉慧">李嘉慧</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$li-teng-90-81" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/li-teng-90-81" class="zg-link" title="李腾">李腾</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


